	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=193711><span id= >technoeq</span></a><br><span id=notbold>33 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.44]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Here's the thing folks.&nbsp;&nbsp;10 wins will probably NOT make your stone show any stats.  I think I had to have 20 just for mine to say 1 HP 1 MANA.  Be patient, for every 10 wins at one camp your stone will grow in power but the stats don't show up until you put the stone on a charm.  I have over 100 wins and my stone is 1 AC 1 to all stats and saves and 17 HP 17 Mana.  Want more stats, do more adventures in different camps. And don't check your stone in the zone you are in when you hail the guy, usually it won't show any changes until you zone.</p>&nbsp;<br> </td></td></tr>
