	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=228006><span id=Scholar>Xaritus</span></a><br><b><span id=Scholar>Scholar</span></b><br><span id=notbold>23 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.45]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>As has been stated below, you are not getting full stats because of your level (the stone is Rec level 65).&nbsp;&nbsp;At 65, for every 10 wins, you get +1/5 all stats and saves (but it doesn't give you the stats until you reach the first whole number, which is the 5th stone upgrade if you do 10 in each camp) and +2hp/mana.  So after 50 wins, it should be +1 all stats and saves and +10 hp/mana at level 65.<br><br>Xaritus<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Tue Apr 13 17:17:11 2004</em></p>&nbsp;<br> </td></td></tr>
